sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Initiator
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Architect
    participant Implementer
    participant Auditor
    participant Verifier
    participant Curator

    %% Bootstrap
    Initiator->>Orchestrator: Deliver validated tranche preamble
    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Validate bootstrap state<br/>folders, envelopes, metadata

    %% Interpretation
    Orchestrator->>Architect: Request Initial DECOR<br/>decor.md + metadata
    Architect-->>Orchestrator: Return Initial DECOR
    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Initialise Ticket Map<br/>tickets + sequencing
    Architect->>Architect: Apply selected DECOR grounding strategy<br/>within Interpretation

    %% Implementation (Ticket Loop)
    loop For each ticket
        Orchestrator->>Implementer: Dispatch ticket<br/>with DECOR subset + metadata
        Implementer->>Implementer: Execute ticket<br/>code, tests, session-logs/, replay-traces/
        Implementer-->>Orchestrator: Return outputs<br/>session-logs/ + replay-traces/ + surfaced truths
        Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Validate acceptance criteria
    end

    %% Reconciliation
    Orchestrator->>Auditor: Provide all tranche artefacts
    Auditor->>Auditor: Classify drift<br/>gov / invariant / arch / impl / test / doc / naming / namespace / identity
    Auditor->>Architect: Request structural reconciliation
    Architect-->>Auditor: Return DECOR updates
    Auditor->>Orchestrator: Deliver Reconciled DECOR draft

    %% Verification
    Orchestrator->>Verifier: Provide artefacts for verification
    Verifier->>Verifier: Execute golden, dark, governance, replay tests
    Verifier-->>Orchestrator: Verification results

    %% Closure
    Orchestrator->>Curator: Submit closure-report.md + tranche artefacts
    Curator-->>Orchestrator: Approve closure
